#. Tag: title
#: useractions.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>UserActions</title>"
msgstr "<title>Uporabniška dejanja</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: useractions.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>UserActions</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Uporabniška dejanja</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With ActionMan you can set up, configure and manage UserActions. Some "
"general settings are configured with <link linkend=\"konfig-useractions"
"\">Konfigurator</link>. With UserActions you can perform actions on files in "
"the panel or to access &krusader; internal functions with parameters "
"directly using placeholders. The actions integrate seamlessly into &plasma; "
"action system, which means that the standard Edit Toolbar and Edit Shortcut "
"dialogs will show UserActions, too. The UserActions are stored in <filename> "
"~/.local/share/krusader/useractions.xml</filename> or <filename>krusader/"
"useraction.xml</filename> in the folder which can be determined using the "
"<userinput>qtpaths --paths GenericDataLocation</userinput> command. Several "
"<link linkend=\"useraction-xml\">examples</link> are included in the "
"documentation. UserActions can be edited / added / imported / exported by "
"using ActionMan. The default UserActions are stored in <filename> /usr/share/"
"krusader/useraction-examples.xml</filename>. UserActions can appear nearly "
"everywhere where <quote>normal</quote> KActions can be placed. The actions "
"can even be placed in the menu bar, but for that the <filename>krusaderui."
"rc</filename> file must be edited. A few examples:"
msgstr ""
"Z ActionMan lahko nastavite, konfigurirate in upravljate UserActions. "
"Nekatere splošne nastavitve se konfigurirajo s <link linkend=\"konfig-"
"useractions\">Konfiguratorjem</link>. Z UserActions lahko izvajate dejanja "
"nad datotekami na plošči ali za dostop do &krusader; notranje funkcije s "
"parametri neposredno z ogradami. Dejanja se neopazno integrirajo v &plasma; "
"akcijski sistem, kar pomeni, da bosta standardna pogovorna okna Urejanje "
"orodne vrstice in Urejanje bližnjice prav tako prikazala Uporabniška "
"dejanja. Uporabniška dejanja so shranjena v <filename> ~/.local/share/"
"krusader/useractions.xml</filename> ali <filename>krusader/useractions.xml</"
"filename> v mapi, ki jo je mogoče določiti s pomočjo <userinput>qtpaths --"
"paths GenericDataLocation</userinput> ukaz. V dokumentacijo je vključenih "
"več <link linkend=\"useraction-xml\">primerov</link>. Uporabniška dejanja je "
"mogoče urejati/dodati/uvažati/izvažati z uporabo ActionMan. Privzeta "
"uporabniška dejanja so shranjena v <filename> /usr/share/krusader/useraction-"
"examples.xml</filename>. Uporabniška dejanja se lahko pojavijo skoraj "
"povsod, kjer je mogoče postaviti <quote>normalne</quote> KAkcije. Dejanja "
"lahko postavite celo v menijsko vrstico, vendar je za to treba urediti "
"datoteko <filename>krusaderui.rc</filename>. Nekaj primerov:"

#. Tag: link
#: useractions.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "Useractions Menu"
msgstr "Meni uporabniških dejanj"

#. Tag: link
#: useractions.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Menu"
msgstr "Uporabniški meni"

#. Tag: link
#: useractions.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actions Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica dejanj"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "right click menus"
msgstr "meniji z desnim klikom"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "&etc;"
msgstr "&etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader;'s UserActions tool is very powerful and customizable if you are "
"familiar with writing UserActions in general."
msgstr ""
"&krusader;ovo orodje UserActions je zelo zmogljivo in prilagodljivo, če ste "
"seznanjeni s pisanjem UserActions na splošno."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several UserActions are provided by default. Please <link linkend="
"\"help_krusader\">upload your favorite UserActions</link> so that they "
"become available for the &krusader; community. Thanks!"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je na voljo več uporabniških dejanj. Prosimo <link linkend="
"\"help_krusader\">naložite svoja priljubljena uporabniška dejanja</link>, da "
"bodo na voljo za &krusader; skupnosti. Hvala!"

#. Tag: title
#: useractions.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>ActionMan</title>"
msgstr "<title>ActionMan</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: useractions.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>ActionMan</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>ActionMan</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Basically, UserActions are a method to call external programs with variable "
"parameters. For example, you could have a UserAction with the following "
"<command>xmms <option>--enqueue %aList(\"Selected\")%</option></command> to "
"enqueue all selected items of the active panel to the current instance of "
"xmms. Additionally, there is limited access to &krusader; internal functions "
"requiring parameters. For example, <command>%aPanelSize(\"80\")%</command> "
"will set the width of the active panel to 80% of the &krusader; mainwindow. "
"Since the parameter of placeholders can contain other placeholders, few "
"scripts are possible."
msgstr ""
"V bistvu so UserActions metoda za klicanje zunanjih programov s "
"spremenljivimi parametri. Na primer, lahko bi imeli UserAction z naslednjim "
"<command>xmms <option>--enqueue %aList(\"Selected\")%</option></command>, da "
"vse izbrane elemente aktivne plošče postavite v čakalno vrsto na trenutni "
"primerek od xmms. Poleg tega je dostop do &krusader; notranje funkcije, ki "
"zahtevajo parametre. Na primer, <command>%aPanelSize(\"80\")%</command> bo "
"nastavil širino aktivne plošče na 80 % širine &krusader; glavno okno. Ker "
"parameter ograd lahko vsebuje druge ograde, je možnih nekaj skriptov."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: useractions.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing UserActions"
msgstr "Upravljanje uporabniških dejanj"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open Konfigurator and choose <menuchoice><guimenu>User Actions</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Start ActionMan</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, in which you can "
"add, edit, remove, import and export UserActions."
msgstr ""
"Odprite Konfigurator in izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Uporabniška dejanja</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zaženi ActionMan</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, v katerem "
"lahko dodajate, urejate, odstranjujete, uvažate in izvažate uporabniška "
"dejanja."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Add Action</guimenuitem>: If you add an new action, you get an "
"empty input mask where you can enter all the properties you desire. The "
"action will be added as soon as you press <guimenuitem>Apply</guimenuitem>. "
"Afterwards, the name is shown in the list on the left."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Dodaj dejanje</guimenuitem>: Če dodate novo dejanje, dobite "
"prazno vnosno masko, kjer lahko vnesete vse želene lastnosti. Dejanje bo "
"dodano takoj, ko pritisnete <guimenuitem>Uporabi</guimenuitem>. Nato se ime "
"prikaže na seznamu na levi."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit a UserAction: Select the UserAction on the left. Then choose it if "
"you want to edit its properties. The changes will only take effect when you "
"press <guimenuitem>Apply</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti UserAction: Izberite UserAction na levi. Nato ga izberite, "
"če želite urediti njegove lastnosti. Spremembe bodo začele veljati šele, ko "
"pritisnete <guimenuitem>Uporabi</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>To remove a UserAction</guimenuitem>: Select the UserAction on "
"the left and click the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>button."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Če želite odstraniti UserAction</guimenuitem>: Izberite "
"UserAction na levi in kliknite <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject > </"
"inlinemediaobject>gumb."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>To import a UserAction</guimenuitem>: If you import some "
"actions, they will be automatically added to your list. If there are name "
"conflicts (the names have to be unique because these are the ID for &plasma; "
"action system), you are asked to resolve them. For this, the list on the "
"left will only show the actions where conflicts exist. You can now give them "
"new names or remove them."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Za uvoz uporabniškega dejanja</guimenuitem>: Če uvozite nekaj "
"dejanj, bodo samodejno dodana na vaš seznam. Če pride do navzkrižja imen "
"(imena morajo biti unikatna, ker so to ID za &plasma; akcijski sistem), "
"boste pozvani, da jih razrešite. Za to bodo na seznamu na levi prikazana "
"samo dejanja, kjer obstajajo spori. Zdaj jim lahko daste nova imena ali jih "
"odstranite."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Export Action</guimenuitem>: If you export a UserAction you "
"have to give a filename in which to store it. If it does not exist, it will "
"be created. If the file already contains UserActions, the action you are "
"exporting will be added to that file."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Dejanje izvoza</guimenuitem>: Če izvozite dejanje uporabnika, "
"morate dati ime datoteke, v katero ga želite shraniti. Če ne obstaja, bo "
"ustvarjen. Če datoteka že vsebuje UserActions, bo dejanje, ki ga izvažate, "
"dodano tej datoteki."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All actions you have defined are now shown in the user menu and in &plasma; "
"dialogs for changing shortcuts and managing the toolbar. In addition, all "
"actions available for the current item will also show up in the right click "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"Vsa dejanja, ki ste jih določili, so zdaj prikazana v uporabniškem meniju in "
"v &plasma; pogovorna okna za spreminjanje bližnjic in upravljanje orodne "
"vrstice. Poleg tega se bodo v meniju z desnim klikom prikazala tudi vsa "
"dejanja, ki so na voljo za trenutni element."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: useractions.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Basic Properties"
msgstr "Osnovne lastnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Identifier</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Title</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Command line</guimenuitem> are always required, all the other "
"properties are optional."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Identifikator</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Naslov</guimenuitem> "
"in <guimenuitem>Ukazna vrstica</guimenuitem> so vedno potrebni, vse druge "
"lastnosti so neobvezne."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Identifier</guimenuitem>: A unique name of the UserAction, used "
"to identify it for &plasma; action system."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Identifikator</guimenuitem>: enolično ime UserAction, ki se "
"uporablja za identifikacijo za &plasma; akcijski sistem."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Icon button</guimenuitem>: The icon for your UserAction."
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Gumb ikone</guimenuitem>: Ikona za vaše UserAction."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Category</guimenuitem>: Categories are used for a better "
"overview. They appear as submenu items in the <guimenuitem>Useractions</"
"guimenuitem> menu."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Kategorija</guimenuitem>: Kategorije se uporabljajo za boljši "
"pregled. Pojavijo se kot elementi podmenija v meniju "
"<guimenuitem>Uporabniške akcije</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Title</guimenuitem>: The title displayed in the menus or "
"dialogs."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Naslov</guimenuitem>: naslov, prikazan v menijih ali pogovornih "
"oknih."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Tooltip</guimenuitem>: A tooltip for your UserAction, &eg; "
"displayed in the toolbar on mouseover."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Namig orodja</guimenuitem>: Namig orodja za vaše UserAction, "
"&eg; prikazano v orodni vrstici ob prehodu miške."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Description</guimenuitem>: A description of what the UserAction "
"does. This is also displayed as <guimenuitem>What's This</guimenuitem> if "
"you <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo> click "
"on your UserAction."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Opis</guimenuitem>: Opis, kaj naredi UserAction. To je "
"prikazano tudi kot <guimenuitem>Kaj je to</guimenuitem>, če <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo> kliknite svoje UserAction."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Command</guimenuitem>: The command which will be executed. You "
"can add placeholder using a &GUI; with the <guibutton>add</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Ukaz</guimenuitem>: Ukaz, ki bo izveden. Oznako mesta lahko "
"dodate z &GUI; z gumbom <guibutton>dodaj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Workdir</guimenuitem>: The working folder for the command which "
"will be executed."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Delovni imenik</guimenuitem>: Delovna mapa za ukaz, ki bo "
"izveden."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Execution mode</guimenuitem>:"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Način izvajanja</guimenuitem>:"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Normal</guimenuitem>: Normal execution mode."
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Normalno</guimenuitem>: Običajen način izvajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Run in terminal</guimenuitem>: Runs the command in the terminal."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Zaženi v terminalu</guimenuitem>: Zažene ukaz v terminalu."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Run in embedded terminal emulator</guimenuitem>: Runs the "
"command in the embedded terminal."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Zaženi v vdelanem terminalskem emulatorju</guimenuitem>: Zažene "
"ukaz v vdelanem terminalu."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Collect output</guimenuitem>: Collects the output of the "
"executed program in a &GUI; window."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Zberi izhodne podatke</guimenuitem>: Zbere izhodne podatke "
"izvedenega programa v &GUI; okno."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Separate standard error</guimenuitem>: When <quote>Collect "
"output</quote> is used the stdout and stderr are separately collected."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Ločena standardna napaka</guimenuitem>: Ko je uporabljen "
"<quote>Zberi izhod</quote>, se stdout in stderr zbirata ločeno."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Command accepts</guimenuitem>:"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Ukaz sprejema</guimenuitem>:"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Local files only (no &URL;s)</guimenuitem>: Tells the "
"placeholder it should return local addresses."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Samo lokalne datoteke (brez &URL;-jev)</guimenuitem>: "
"nadomestnemu znaku pove, da mora vrniti lokalne naslove."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>&URL;s (remote and local)</guimenuitem>: Tells the placeholder "
"it should return &URL;s."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>&URL;-ji (oddaljeni in lokalni)</guimenuitem>: pove označbi "
"mesta, da mora vrniti &URL;-je."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Default shortcut</guimenuitem>: Configures a default shortcut "
"for the UserAction."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Privzeta bližnjica</guimenuitem>: Konfigurira privzeto "
"bližnjico za UserAction."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Enabled</guimenuitem>: if checked, the useraction is shown in "
"the <link linkend=\"useractions\">User Menu</link>, otherwise the useraction "
"will be hidden."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Omogočeno</guimenuitem>: če je označeno, je dejanje uporabnika "
"prikazano v <link linkend=\"useractions\">uporabniškem meniju</link>, sicer "
"bo dejanje uporabnika skrito."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: useractions.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command-line syntax"
msgstr "Sintaksa ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Basically, everything you type in the command line will get executed (if you "
"type <quote>ls -l</quote>, <quote>ls -l</quote> gets executed). You have the "
"possibility to get a character string from &krusader; which represents the "
"current state of the panel. This is done using placeholders. A placeholder "
"begins with a percent-sign ('%') and is followed by a panel indicator ('a' "
"for the active, 'o' for the other, 'l' for the left and 'r' for the right "
"panel. If the placeholder does not need a panel to operate on, you have to "
"indicate this by an underscore ('_')). Then comes the name of the "
"placeholder (see the list below), which may get some parameters enclosed in "
"quotes. Finally, again the percent sign."
msgstr ""
"V bistvu se izvede vse, kar vnesete v ukazno vrstico (če vnesete <quote>ls -"
"l</quote>, se izvede <quote>ls -l</quote>). Imate možnost pridobiti niz "
"znakov iz &krusader; ki predstavlja trenutno stanje plošče. To se naredi z "
"uporabo nadomestnih mest. Oznaka mesta se začne z znakom za odstotek ('%'), "
"sledi pa mu indikator plošče ('a' za aktivno, 'o' za drugo, 'l' za levo in "
"'r' za desno ploščo. Če nadomestni znak ne potrebuje plošče za delovanje, "
"morate to označiti s podčrtajem ('_')). Nato sledi ime nadomestnega znaka "
"(glejte spodnji seznam), ki lahko dobi nekatere parametre v narekovajih. Na "
"koncu spet znak za odstotek."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This sounds very complicated, so let's make an example: '%aList(\"Selected"
"\")%' is replaced by a list of all selected items in the active panel. So a "
"command like 'xmms --enqueue %aList(\"All\", \" \", \"\", \"*.mp3\")%' will "
"execute xmms with a list of all .mp3s in the current panel, separated by a "
"single blank."
msgstr ""
"To zveni zelo zapleteno, zato naredimo primer: '%aList(\"Selected\")%' je "
"nadomeščen s seznamom vseh izbranih elementov v aktivni plošči. Torej bo "
"ukaz, kot je 'xmms --enqueue %aList(\"All\", \" \", \"\", \"*.mp3\")%' "
"izvedel xmms s seznamom vseh .mp3-jev na trenutni plošči, ločenih z enim "
"samim praznim mestom ."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Currently, these placeholders are implemented:"
msgstr "Trenutno so implementirani ti nadomestni znaki:"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>Path</userinput> - replaced by the panels path"
msgstr "<userinput>Pot</userinput> - zamenjana s potjo plošč"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:295 useractions.docbook:327 useractions.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter (optional): Automatic escape spaces. Default: yes"
msgstr "Parameter (izbirno): Samodejni prostori za pobeg. Privzeto: da"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Count</userinput> - replaced by the number of &lt;first "
"parameter&gt;"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Štetje</userinput> - zamenjano s številko &lt;prvega parametra&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:307 useractions.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter: Which items; either <quote>All</quote>, <quote>Selected</quote>, "
"<quote>Files</quote> or <quote>Dirs</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Parameter: kateri predmeti; <quote>Vse</quote>, <quote>Izbrano</quote>, "
"<quote>Datoteke</quote> ali <quote>Imeniki</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>Filter</userinput> - replaced by the panel's filter mask"
msgstr "<userinput>Filter</userinput> - nadomeščen z masko filtra plošče"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>Current</userinput> - replaced by the current item"
msgstr "<userinput>Trenutno</userinput> - zamenjano s trenutnim elementom"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:323 useractions.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter (optional): Omit the current path. Default: no"
msgstr "Parameter (izbirno): Izpustite trenutno pot. Privzeto: ne"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>List</userinput> - replaced by a list of all &lt;first "
"parameter&gt;"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Seznam</userinput> - nadomeščen s seznamom vseh &lt;prvih "
"parametrov&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter (optional): Separator between the items. Default: <quote>&nbsp;</"
"quote>"
msgstr ""
"Parameter (izbirno): ločilo med postavkami. Privzeto: <quote>&nbsp;</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter (optional): Filtermask (for all but <quote>Selected</quote>). "
"Default: *"
msgstr ""
"Parameter (izbirno): Filtermask (za vse, razen za <quote>Izbrano</quote>). "
"Privzeto: *"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>Select</userinput> - manipulates the selection in a panel"
msgstr "<userinput>Izberi</userinput> - manipulira z izbiro na plošči"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter: Filtermask"
msgstr "Parameter: Filtermask"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter (optional): manipulate in which way; either <quote>Set</quote>, "
"<quote>Add</quote> or <quote>Remove</quote>. Default: <quote>Set</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Parameter (izbirno): manipulirajte na kakšen način; <quote>Nastavi</quote>, "
"<quote>Dodaj</quote> ali <quote>Odstrani</quote>. Privzeto: <quote>Nastavi</"
"quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Goto</userinput> - changes the panels' path to &lt;first "
"parameter&gt;"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Pojdi</userinput> - spremeni pot plošč na &lt;prvi parameter&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter: A relative or absolute path, or an &URL;"
msgstr "Parameter: relativna ali absolutna pot ali &URL;"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter (optional): Open the location in a new tab. Default: no"
msgstr "Parameter (neobvezno): odpri lokacijo v novem zavihku. Privzeto: ne"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Ask</userinput> - asks the user for some text and is replaced by "
"the answer"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Vprašaj</userinput> - od uporabnika zahteva nekaj besedila, ki ga "
"nadomesti odgovor"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:401
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter: The Question"
msgstr "Parameter: vprašanje"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter (optional): A default answer"
msgstr "Parameter (izbirno): privzeti odgovor"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter (optional): A caption for the question box"
msgstr "Parameter (izbirno): napis za polje z vprašanji"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>Clipboard</userinput> - manipulates the clipboard"
msgstr "<userinput>Odložišče</userinput> - upravlja z odložiščem"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter: The text that should go to the clipboard (you may want to use "
"<quote>%aCurrent%</quote> here)"
msgstr ""
"Parameter: Besedilo, ki naj gre v odložišče (tukaj boste morda želeli "
"uporabiti <quote>%aCurrent%</quote>)"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter (optional): Append the text to the current content of the "
"clipboard with this separator"
msgstr ""
"Parameter (neobvezno): pripni besedilo trenutni vsebini odložišča s tem "
"ločilom"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Copy</userinput> - copies a file, useful for quick, local backups"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Kopiraj</userinput> - kopira datoteko, uporabno za hitre lokalne "
"varnostne kopije"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter: What should be copied"
msgstr "Parameter: Kaj naj se kopira"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter: Where it should be copied"
msgstr "Parameter: Kam naj se kopira"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Sync</userinput> - opens the Synchronizer with a given profile"
msgstr "<userinput>Sync</userinput> - odpre sinhronizator z danim profilom"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter: A profile for the Synchronizer"
msgstr "Parameter: Profil za sinhronizator"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>NewSearch</userinput> - opens the search windows with a given "
"profile"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Novo iskanje</userinput> - odpre iskalna okna z danim profilom"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter: A profile for the search module"
msgstr "Parameter: Profil za iskalni modul"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>Profile</userinput> - loads a given panel profile"
msgstr "<userinput>Profil</userinput> - naloži dani profil plošče"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter: A panel profile"
msgstr "Parameter: Profil plošče"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Each</userinput> - splits the commandline into a list. These "
"commands are executed one after another."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Vsak</userinput> - razdeli ukazno vrstico na seznam. Ti ukazi se "
"izvajajo drug za drugim."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter: A list item (all, all files, all dirs, all selected)."
msgstr ""
"Parameter: Element seznama (vse, vse datoteke, vsi imeniki, vsi izbrani)."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>Move</userinput> - move from source to destination."
msgstr "<userinput>Premakni</userinput> - premakni se od vira do cilja."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter: A source"
msgstr "Parameter: vir"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter: A destination"
msgstr "Parameter: Cilj"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>PanelSize</userinput> - change the ratio between the two panels."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Velikost plošče</userinput> - spremenite razmerje med obema "
"ploščama."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter (optional): A integer value, &eg;, 80 makes the active panel use "
"80% of &krusader;'s width (height in vertical mode), omitting the parameter "
"means 50%."
msgstr ""
"Parameter (neobvezno): celoštevilska vrednost, &eg; 80, omogoči, da aktivna "
"plošča uporabi 80 % širine (višine v navpičnem načinu) &krusader;, "
"izpustitev parametra pomeni 50 %."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>Ask</userinput> - cancel the execution."
msgstr "<userinput>Vprašaj</userinput> - prekliči izvedbo."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter (optional): A string for the cancel question."
msgstr "Parameter (izbirno): niz za vprašanje za preklic."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>ListFile</userinput> - is replaced by path/file name of a "
"temporary file containing a list of items"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>ListFile</userinput> - zamenja se z imenom poti/datoteke začasne "
"datoteke, ki vsebuje seznam elementov"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameter: path/filename"
msgstr "Parameter: pot/ime datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>ColSort</userinput> - set the sorting on a column of a specific "
"panel."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>ColSort</userinput> - nastavite razvrščanje v stolpcu določene "
"plošče."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter: Column: Either <quote>Name</quote>, <quote>Ext</quote>, "
"<quote>Type</quote>, <quote>Size</quote>, <quote>Modified</quote>, "
"<quote>Perms</quote>, <quote>rwx</quote>, <quote>Owner</quote> and "
"<quote>Group</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Parameter: Stolpec: <quote>Ime</quote>, <quote>Zunanja</quote>, "
"<quote>Vrsta</quote>, <quote>Velikost</quote>, <quote>Spremenjeno</quote>, "
"<quote>Dovoljenja</quote>, <quote>rwx</quote>, <quote>Lastnik</quote> in "
"<quote>Skupina</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter: Sort sequence: Either <quote>Toggle</quote>, <quote>Asc</quote>, "
"<quote>Desc</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Parameter: Zaporedje razvrščanja: bodisi <quote>Toggle</quote>, <quote>Asc</"
"quote>, <quote>Desc</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>View</userinput> - set the view mode."
msgstr "<userinput>Pogled</userinput> - nastavite način pogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter: View mode: Either <quote>generic</quote>, <quote>text</quote>, "
"<quote>hex</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Parameter: Način pogleda: <quote>generično</quote>, <quote>besedilno</"
"quote>, <quote>šestnajstiško</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter: Window Mode: Either <quote>tab</quote>, <quote>window</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Parameter: okenski način: bodisi <quote>zavihek</quote>, <quote>okno</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A &GUI;-based helper for placeholder adding is provided. Spaces in Path, "
"Current and List are by default, automatically escaped. There is one more "
"important thing to know: All placeholders that interact with &krusader; "
"internal functions are called at expand time (meaning directly when the "
"placeholders are replaced). External programs are called at execution time "
"(meaning after all placeholders are replaced)."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo je pomočnik za dodajanje ograd, ki temelji na &GUI;. Presledki v "
"možnostih Pot, Trenutno in Seznam so privzeto samodejno ubežni. Vedeti "
"morate še eno pomembno stvar: vse ogradne oznake, ki sodelujejo z &krusader; "
"notranje funkcije se kličejo v času razširitve (kar pomeni neposredno, ko se "
"zamenjajo ograde). Zunanji programi so priklicani v času izvajanja (kar "
"pomeni, ko so zamenjane vse ograde)."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: useractions.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Properties"
msgstr "Napredne lastnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can configure where your command should be visible (for the right "
"click menu). In addition, it is possible to change the command executed and "
"confirm it separately. You can also set a user under which the command "
"should be executed."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko konfigurirate, kje naj bo vaš ukaz viden (za meni z desnim "
"klikom). Poleg tega je mogoče spremeniti izvedeni ukaz in ga posebej "
"potrditi. Nastavite lahko tudi uporabnika, pod katerim naj se izvede ukaz."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configures if the action is valid for a Protocol, Path, &MIME; type or File "
"name."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurira, ali je dejanje veljavno za protokol, pot, &MIME; vrsto ali Ime "
"datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tweaking the command line before being executed."
msgstr "Prilagoditev ukazne vrstice pred izvedbo."

#. Tag: para
#: useractions.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set a different user for the execution (this has no effect in &krusader; "
"internal functions)"
msgstr ""
"Nastavite drugega uporabnika za izvajanje (to nima vpliva na notranje "
"funkcije &krusader;)"
